<p>Sunday 10/6/17<br/>Tactical schemes all day without troops. Battalion at musketry.<br/>Monday 11/6/17<br/>Training generally, rumours of move.<br/>Tuesday 12/6/17<br/>Usual training, orders to move on Saturday.<br/>Wednesday 13/6/17<br/>Training in morning, cricket match against 27th in afternoon, won by us.<br/>Thursday 14/6/17<br/>Training generally. Concert at night at Bouzincourt &ndash; purchased the Anzac Coves for the night.<br/>Friday 15/6/17<br/>Defeated 7th Eng at Cricket. Field firing in afternoon, dined at Corps School.</p>
